commit message: fix fairly stupid bug with custom routes
Add UI/config parsing for excluded routes
add notice about need of OpenVPN support
Fix bugs with the ocnfig parser
Fix lint issue with web view
More fine tuning of file import for 4.3/add hint for selecting files

Move to new gradle project structure (drop Eclipse support, add initial remote demo project)
